resources.description: NetMagic is an open hardware platform facing the internet research and the teaching of network, which is widely applied to the new network technique. The dissertation took the study of technology of precise delay measurement based on NetMagic, then put forword the idea of carrying timestamp by means of SMAC and brought it into force, moreover, we fulfill its corresponding measurement.
resources.name: Precise Delay Measurement Based on NetMagic
